        "headline": "Swiss PGDay 2026: Announcement and CfS",
        "content": {
          "excerpt_text": "We are pleased to announce Swiss PGDay 2026 , which will take place on Thursday 25 June and Friday 26 June 2026 at the OST Eastern Switzerland University of Applied Sciences, Campus Rapperswil (near Zurich) . The two-day conference will have two tracks. Presentations will mainly be in English, but there will also be some in German (with at least one in English in each time slot). To encourage networking in the community, a social event will be organised at the end of the first day of the...",
