        "updated_at": "2026-03-03T00:00:00Z",
        "headline": "Autobase 2.6.0 released",
        "content": {
          "excerpt_text": "Autobase 2.6 introduces a blue-green deployment workflow that allows you to prepare a fully upgraded cluster in advance and switch traffic with near-zero downtime. Instead of upgrading your production cluster directly, you can: deploy a clone of the cluster (Patroni standby cluster), synchronize data using physical replication, automatically upgrade PostgreSQL on the target cluster, convert it into a logical replica, and continue receiving live changes from production until switchover. When...",
          "lang": "en"
        },
