        "updated_at": "2026-03-03T00:00:00Z",
        "headline": "Pg_QoS v1.0.0 stable release is out!",
        "content": {
          "excerpt_text": "We are pleased to announce the first stable release of Pg_QoS , a PostgreSQL extension that provides Quality of Service (QoS) style resource governance for sessions and queries. 🔹 Project overview Enforce per-role and per-database limits via ALTER ROLE/DATABASE SET qos.* Limit CPU usage by binding the backend to N CPU cores (Linux only); planner integration ensures parallel workers stay within that cap Track and cap concurrent transactions and statements (SELECT/UPDATE/DELETE/INSERT)...",
          "lang": "en"
        },
