        "headline": "PostgresCompare 1.1.104 Released",
        "content": {
          "excerpt_text": "PostgresCompare is pleased to announce the release of version 1.1.104, along with a summary of recent highlights from 1.1.103. PostgresCompare connects to two live PostgreSQL databases, detects schema differences across tables, views, functions, indexes, types, and 30+ other object types, and generates a ready-to-run SQL deployment script to synchronise them. It runs on Windows, macOS, and Linux. New in 1.1.104 Pre/post deploy scripts — Projects can now include custom SQL that runs before...",
